Package: reasonbench
Title: Reasonably Perfect Benchmarks for ML Models
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Diogo", "Ribeiro", email = "contact@diogoribeiro.ai", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a robust and extensible framework to evaluate machine learning models 
    against realistic benchmarks. Implements the concept of 'reasonably-perfect' models 
    that simulate achievable performance limits under data uncertainty.
